hopobject.body: I'm interested in this position herbal essences ignite my color One day we made a trip to Padua to see the breathtaking Giotto fresco at Cappella degli Scrovegni and visit the excellent museum. On another we ventured to Vicenza to admire the Teatro Olimpico and other buildings by Palladio. We also headed off early (but as it transpired not early enough) one morning to Lake Garda, an outing that almost ended in disaster when we drove around for an hour looking for a parking space (to a backdrop of wailing children, which stoked up the emotional temperature nicely).
